  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Strengthening Dialogue for Peace and Reconciliation in South Sudan</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will strengthen the role of mass media specifically radio and online news which are the most accessible source of information in South Sudan in the peace-building process, from merely reporting issues and events to: (a) understanding and clarifying issues and events from diverse perspectives including historical and sociopolitical contexts; (b) informing and educating the public on history, culture, political structure, and aspirations of various ethnic groups as a means of promoting cultural understanding and appreciation; and (c) providing a platform for expressing views and opinions, dialogue and consensus-building within and among different communities.</narrative>
  </description>
